code: @Override public Exchange aggregate(Exchange oldExchange, Exchange newExchange) {     if (oldExchange == null) {         // for the first time we must create a new empty exchange as the         // holder, as the outgoing exchange         // must not be one of the grouped exchanges, as that causes a         // endless circular reference         oldExchange = new DefaultExchange(newExchange).     }     return super.aggregate(oldExchange, newExchange). }
@Override public Message getValue(Exchange exchange) {     return exchange.getIn(). }
